import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { withRouter } from 'react-router' import { Input, Row } from 'antd' const Navbar = ({ history }) => { const route = history?.location?.pathname || window.location.pathname const noNavPage = ['/signup', '/login'] if (noNavPage.includes(route)) return null const title = 'Foodie' return ( <>
{title}
{/* if logged in -> show logout and home if not logged in show login signup */}
) } export default withRouter(Navbar)
